<lb n="0835a26" ed="T"/>欽<note place="inline">忻州<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0835002" n="0835002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0835002" n="0835002"/>空<anchor xml:id="end0835002"/>襄縣</note>　檀命暉<note place="inline">五臺縣</note>　五茂林　陽喜
<lb n="0835a27" ed="T"/>子<note place="inline">唐林縣</note>　雍日新</p>
<lb n="0835a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT52p0835a2801">聖玉花寺造寺都料</p>
